Which of the following C code snippets correctly defines the `main` function with a code block?

**Option 1:**

```c
main()
    printf("Hello!");
```

**Option 2:**

```c
main() {
    printf("Hello!");
}
```

**Option 3:**

```c
main() [
    printf("Hello!");
]
```

**Option 4:**

```c
main {
    printf("Hello!");
}
```

